sql:
SELECT p.name, ia.impact_score
FROM projects p
INNER JOIN impact_assessments ia ON p.project_id = ia.project_id;

external_knowledge:
- The "significance of their impact" can be understood as the impact score given to the projects; 
- The "shortform of the organization" refers to the abbreviated name of the organization;
- "Recent assessments" means the latest assessment dates for these projects.

